limpid.y_reset_internal.comment: Internal connector for controller output reset

limpid.Nd.comment: The higher Nd, the more ideal the derivative block

limpid.Ni.comment: Ni*Ti is time constant of anti-windup compensation

limpid.P.k.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

limpid.gainPID.k.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

limpid.gainTrack.k.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

limpid.revAct.comment: Switch for sign for reverse or direct acting controller

limpid.xd_start.comment: Initial or guess value for state of derivative block

limpid.xi_start.comment: Initial or guess value value for integrator output (= integrator state)

limpid.y_reset.comment: Value to which the controller output is reset if the boolean trigger has a rising edge, used if reset == Buildings.Types.Reset.Parameter

limpid.initType.comment: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3: initial state, 4: initial output)

limpid.limiter.strict.comment: = true, if strict limits with noEvent(..)
